### Create a direct conversation
POST https://localhost/conversations/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "direct",
  "owners": [
    "68fba170e3d051cfa1e4a94b", 
    "68f7bf08e5780a024d105b3c"
  ],
  "metadata": {
    "autoDeleteTime": 600
  }
}

### Create a group conversation
POST http://localhost/conversations/
Content-Type: application/json

### Join the conversation
POST http://localhost/conversations/cid/join
Content-Type: application/json

### Get participants of the conversation
GET https://localhost/conversations/693909e0704c96d28e612a09/participants 

### Get messages of the conversation
GET https://localhost/conversations/693d273e3b0297bd1fa917c8/messages

### Get messages of the conversation
GET https://localhost/conversations/68fba182e3d051cfa1e4a94c/invitation
Content-Type: application/json

